        <body>
            
            <div type="edition">            	
                
                <div n="A" type="textpart" xml:lang="fra-Latn" rendition="class:undetermined maturity:undetermined"><head>1st slab</head>
                    <p>
                        <lb n="1"/>PYRAMIDE
                        <lb n="2"/>BATIE
                        <lb n="3"/>AS • AYASSAMY &amp; C<hi rend="superscript">o</hi>
                        <lb n="4"/>1888
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <div n="B" type="textpart" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular"><head>2nd slab</head>
                    <p>
                        <lb n="1"/>Inta kōpuram
                        <lb n="2"/>ye • cu Ayyācāmi
                        <lb n="3"/><g type="piḷḷai"/> kampeṉiyār
                        <lb n="4"/>tarumam·
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div type="apparatus">
                
            </div>
            
            <div type="translation" resp="part:emfr">
                <div n="A" type="textpart"><head>1st slab</head>
                    <p n="1-3">
                        Pyramid built <supplied reason="subaudible">by</supplied> A. S. Ayassamy &amp; C<hi rend="superscript">o</hi>.
                    </p>
                    <p n="4">1888.</p>
                </div>
                <div n="B" type="textpart"><head>2nd slab</head>
                    <p n="1-4">
                        This <foreign>gopura</foreign> <supplied reason="subaudible">is</supplied> a pious donation <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>tarumam</foreign><note>Sanskrit <foreign>dharma</foreign>.</note></supplied> <supplied reason="subaudible">of/by</supplied> Ye. Cu. Ayyācāmi Piḷḷai <supplied reason="subaudible">and</supplied> company <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>kampeṉiyār</foreign><note>Literally: those in his company.</note></supplied>.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="fra" resp="part:emfr">
                
            </div>
            
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The blocks are (in 2025) on the top of the compound wall on both sides of the <foreign>gopura</foreign>. Old pictures show that they were originally on the <foreign>gopura</foreign> itself and moved from there when renovation took place in 2004.</p>
            </div>
            
